Q.15 --> How to insert a picture into a background image of a web page? With Example.

Ans:- 
      
      The most common & simple way to add background image is using the background image attribute inside the <body> tag.
      Second method is create a CSS to add background image.

      Example:

               -> Using <body> tag in Html:

                  <body background="background_image/image1.jpg">


               -> Using CSS in <style> tag in Html:

                <style>
                    body
                    {
                        <!-- background: url('enter a image path') no-repeat; -->
                        background: url('background_image/image1.jpg') no-repeat;
                        background-size: cover;
                        background-attachment: fixed;
                    }
                </style>
             
                